1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,433
This app doesn't ask what you want to do.

2
00:00:02,533 --> 00:00:04,167
It asks who you want to become.

3
00:00:04,267 --> 00:00:09,267
Tell an AI coach your goal, and it builds a real plan.

4
00:00:09,800 --> 00:00:13,367
Milestones and small daily actions.

5
00:00:13,467 --> 00:00:15,267
Check off your day —

6
00:00:15,367 --> 00:00:17,567
and it says so.

7
00:00:17,667 --> 00:00:19,000
Each week, your coach checks in.

8
00:00:19,100 --> 00:00:21,633
Tell it what's hard,

9
00:00:21,733 --> 00:00:26,733
and it adapts the plan to how you're doing.

10
00:00:26,933 --> 00:00:29,933
Resolution Companion — free on the App Store.
